        YOU_HAVE_ALREADY_FOUND_A_LOST_ARTICLE_AS                                      = 7878,  -- You have already found a lost article. As much as it pains you to ignore someone's plight, you decide to deliver the one currently in your possession to the manager in charge of your assignment.
