        HISTORY_IS_ALWAYS_SEEN_THROUGH_THE_EYES_OF                                    = 8733,  -- History is always seen through the eyes of the victor. But as each order considered themselves the winner, we have no fewer than twelve whitewashed versions of what really happened.
