        DID_YOU_SEE_THAT_BEAUTY_WHO_JUST_ARRIVED                                      = 8746,  -- Did you see that beauty who just arrived at the docks? A shame that her heart isn't as pristine as her skin.
        NORMAL_FOLK_CAN_T_RIDE_THE_SHIPS_WITHOUT                                      = 8747,  -- Normal folk can't ride the ships without a special permit. She completely threw the schedule out of whack when she demanded to board, and the crew had to bend over backwards to accommodate her.
        EVERY_ROSE_HAS_ITS_THORNS_BUT_SOME_HAVE                                       = 8748,  -- Every rose has its thorns--but some have more than others.
        COME_TO_THINK_OF_IT_WEREN_T_YOU                                               = 8749,  -- Come to think of it, weren't you supposed to take her to the castle? Then quit skulking about here and get to it!
        HUH_YOU_WANT_A_PIECE_OF_STONE_WALL                                            = 8750,  -- Huh? You want a piece of stone wall touched by the light of dawn?
        SOMETHING_ABOUT_AN_EXORCIST_RITUAL_YOU_SAY_WELL                               = 8751,  -- Something about an exorcist ritual, you say? Well, I'm pretty sure you've come to the right place.
        BUT_THERE_ARE_LOTS_OF_STONES_WHICH_WOULD                                      = 8752,  -- But there are lots of stones. Which would be touched by light?
        I_KNOW_WHERE_YOU_COULD_LOOK_THERE_S                                           = 8753,  -- I know where you could look! There's a grand lighthouse over to the east. Back in the day, people called it the Sunrise Beacon.
        THE_PLACE_YOU_RE_LOOKING_FOR_IS_THE                                           = 8754,  -- The place you're looking for is the Sunrise Beacon, on the east side of the waterfront.
        TELL_ME_HOW_GOES_THE_PIONEERING                                               = 8755,  -- %! Tell me, how goes the pioneering?
        GOOD_TO_HEAR_BUT_SINCE_YOU_RE_HERE                                            = 8756,  -- Good to hear. But since you're here, there's something that's been bothering me.
        IT_S_ABOUT_OUR_BELOVED_PRINCESS                                               = 8757,  -- It's about our beloved princess.
        THE_COLOR_S_DRAINED_FROM_HER_FACE_AND                                         = 8758,  -- The color's drained from her face, and she just mopes about everywhere she goes. She had always been so chipper and upbeat before this.
        YOU_RE_PRETTY_CLOSE_WITH_HER_RIGHT_DO                                         = 8759,  -- You're pretty close with her, right? Do you have any idea what could be wrong?
