        LET_S_CUT_TO_THE_QUICK_JUST_NOW                                               = 8764,  -- Let's cut to the quick. Just now, someone saw Arciela wandering off to the %.
        HER_EYES_WERE_ALL_GLAZED_OVER_AND_UNFOCUSED                                   = 8765,  -- Her eyes were all glazed over and unfocused--I'm worried where she'll stumble off to...and what might find her when she gets there.
