        BUT_IF_YOU_SHEE_HER_CAN_YOU_PLEASHE                                           = 8788,  -- But if you shee her, can you pleashe give her my re...re...regardsh? Pretty pleashe with sugar on top!?
        I_THINK_YOU_VE_GOT_THE_WRONG_IDEA                                             = 8789,  -- I think you've got the wrong idea, missy. She's-- Hey, come back!
        OH_WELL_THERE_S_NO_USE_CHASING_AFTER                                          = 8790,  -- ...Oh, well. There's no use chasing after her just to explain.
        I_KNOW_WE_USE_PRINCESS_AS_A_TERM                                              = 8791,  -- I know we use princess as a term of endearment for her, but I don't think you could even use the phrase constitutional monarchy to describe Adoulin these days. The king himself abolished royal rule long ago.
        I_SUPPOSE_SUCH_CONCEPTS_SOAR_FAR_ABOVE_THE                                    = 8792,  -- I suppose such concepts soar far above the head of a pixie like her, anyway.
