        COUNT_YOUR_LUCKY_STARS_THAT_THE_PRINCESS_IS                                   = 8794,  -- Count your lucky stars that the princess is so knowledgeable about plant life... Come to think of it, I haven't heard about any of her woodland escapades recently.
        I_DON_T_MEAN_TO_PRY_BUT_HOW                                                   = 8795,  -- I don't mean to pry, but how's she faring?
        HOW_IS_ARCIELA_FARING_I_SPOKE_TO_HER                                          = 8796,  -- How is Arciela faring? I spoke to her in the library. She's got a sweet tooth. I asked about guys and what she's into...
        I_SEE_SO_SHE_WAS_THOROUGHLY_ABSORBED_IN                                       = 8797,  -- I see. So, she was thoroughly absorbed in her research and not particularly talkative, then?
        A_SWEET_TOOTH_COULD_SHE_PERHAPS_HAVE_BEEN                                     = 8798,  -- A sweet tooth? Could she perhaps have been worried about them decaying and blemishing her lovely smile? Or maybe she's more concerned about her waistline expanding?
        YOU_MUD_MOUTHED_CUR_HOW_DARE_YOU_SPEAK                                        = 8799,  -- You mud-mouthed cur! How dare you speak so dirty to a lady so pure!?
        HMMM_AT_LEAST_IT_SOUNDS_LIKE_SHE_WAS                                          = 8800,  -- Hmmm... At least it sounds like she was in good spirits.
        THOSE_IN_SUPPORT_OF_THE_COLONIZATION_MOVEMENT_HAVE                            = 8801,  -- Those in support of the colonization movement have not been kind to Arciela, due to her reserved stance on the matter.
        ON_THE_OTHER_HAND_HER_JOURNEYS_INTO_THE                                       = 8802,  -- On the other hand, her journeys into the wilderness do not go over well with her more traditionalist constituents. They fear her much as they would a witch.
        PERHAPS_THINGS_WOULD_BE_DIFFERENT_IF_SHE_SETTLED                              = 8803,  -- Perhaps things would be different if she settled in with a single faction instead of taking the high road and treating everyone as equals. Still, there are people in the Pioneers' Coalition who think the world of her.
        JUST_LIKE_THAT_LITTLE_GIRL_WHO_RAN_OFF                                        = 8804,  -- ...Just like that little girl who ran off a few moments ago.
        MY_POINT_IS_THAT_ARCIELA_MAY_FEEL_ALONE                                       = 8805,  -- My point is that Arciela may feel alone, but she's not. As our representative, stick by her through thick and thin so she knows just how important she is to this city!
        WELL_IF_IT_ISN_T_COME_LOOKING_FOR                                             = 8806,  -- Well, if it isn't %! Come looking for more trouble, no doubt. Wish I had something for you to do, but my slate's as clean as the waters of Fontis Xanira. But wait...you're not really here to see me, are you?
        ARE_YOU_HERE_TO_SEE_HIM_NO_I                                                  = 8807,  -- Are you here to see him? No, I'm looking for someone. Yes, I came to give my regards.
        OH_C_MON_NOW_ALL_OUR_CONVERSATIONS_ARE                                        = 8808,  -- Oh, c'mon now. All our conversations are business-related. Why would this be any different? You know I'd be happy to tell you anything I can.
        ANOTHER_ONE_OF_YOUR_MANHUNTS_IS_IT                                            = 8809,  -- Another one of your manhunts, is it?
        TEODOR_YOU_SAY                                                                = 8810,  -- Teodor, you say?
        OH_RIGHT_THAT_OLD_FUDDY_DUDDY_WHO_S                                           = 8811,  -- Oh, right--that old fuddy-duddy who's always dressed like he's headed for a funeral.
        FUNNY_YOU_SHOULD_MENTION_HIM_ONE_OF_MY                                        = 8812,  -- Funny you should mention him. One of my buddies who fancies himself adept at games of chance was talking the guy up a few days back.
        SOMETHING_ABOUT_COUNTING_CARDS_AND_LOADED_DICE_BAH                            = 8813,  -- Something about counting cards and loaded dice...bah. I tuned him out. But if you're looking for Teodor, I'd check at the Mummers' Coalition.
        BESIDES_WITH_THAT_DOUR_LOOK_PLASTERED_ON_YOUR                                 = 8814,  -- Besides, with that dour look plastered on your face, you could probably use a bit of relaxation.
        ALTANA_LOVES_ALL_HER_CHILDREN_BUT_IT_WOULDN                                   = 8815,  -- Altana loves all her children, but it wouldn't surprise me one bit if that expression makes even her think twice about giving you guidance.
        OFF_YOU_GO_LET_YOUR_HAIR_DOWN_AND                                             = 8816,  -- Off you go. Let your hair down and gamble away some bayld. Everyone needs an escape now and again.
        I_LL_EVEN_GIVE_YOU_A_LITTLE_BIT                                               = 8817,  -- I'll even give you a little bit so you don't have to worry about spending your hard-earned bayld.
        I_DON_T_GET_ENOUGH_TIME_OFF_HERE                                              = 8818,  -- I don't get enough time off here, so I'm counting on you to have enough fun for the both of us!
        THAT_OL_TEODOR_FELLA_HAS_BEEN_MILLING_ABOUT                                   = 8819,  -- That ol' Teodor fella has been milling about the Mummers' Coalition since Arciela was knee-high to a leafkin. No doubt you'll find him there.
        WHILE_YOU_RE_THERE_USE_MY_BAYLD_TO                                            = 8820,  -- While you're there, use my bayld to bring a smile to your face. Wish I could go along, too...but I'm stuck here for a while longer.
        WELL_WELL_MY_DEAREST_PRAY_TELL_HOW_WENT                                       = 8821,  -- Well, well, my dearest %. Pray tell, how went everything with the young lady you were after?
        OH_HO_YOU_SAY_YOU_TEAMED_UP_WITH                                              = 8822,  -- Oh ho, you say you teamed up with our fair princess? The two of you have been seeing a lot of each other lately.
        BUT_ENOUGH_SMALL_TALK_WHAT_CAN_I_DO                                           = 8823,  -- But enough small talk. What can I do for you today?
        I_PRESUME_YOU_DID_NOT_APPROACH_ME_SIMPLY                                      = 8824,  -- I presume you did not approach me simply to stare at my impeccably groomed moustache.
        WHAT_WILL_YOU_ASK_CAN_YOU_HELP_WITH                                           = 8825,  -- What will you ask? Can you help with the Ygnas issue? Well, you do look quite dapper...
        COME_NOW_WE_BOTH_KNOW_THAT_IS_NOT                                             = 8826,  -- Come, now, we both know that is not why you are really here.
        AH_BIT_OF_A_HOT_BUTTON_ISSUE_THESE                                            = 8827,  -- Ah. Bit of a hot-button issue these days. Well, we have had our fair share of dealings of late, and of course I'm inclined to help you...
        HMM_TO_BE_FRANK_I_HAVE_GROWN_BORED                                            = 8828,  -- Hmm... To be frank, I have grown bored with my lot of late.
        AND_ALL_THINGS_HAVE_THEIR_PRICE_AS_AN                                         = 8829,  -- And all things have their price. As an adventurer, you must understand--treasure means more when you overcome adversity to obtain it. In exchange for my aid, I would ask that you play a game with me.
