        P_IQ_5                                                                        = 9202,  -- [b/%1/A(/`&/9b/b/|5D"H"]p%IQ\5=
        HUH_YOU_GOT_SOMETHIN_TO_ASK_ME                                                = 9203,  -- Huh? You got somethin' to ask me?
        WHAT_S_THIS_NOW_YOU_RE_LOOKIN_FER                                             = 9204,  -- What's this now? You're lookin' fer info about them leafkin? Cute little buggers, boy howdy!
        EVERY_TIME_THEY_SEND_ME_OFF_TO_SOME                                           = 9205,  -- Every time they send me off to some frontier station or other I take a quick look fer 'em, but they're too clever to get caught.
        I_GOT_A_MONSTER_OF_A_TALE_FOR                                                 = 9206,  -- I got a monster of a tale for you, though! One time I done seen one down in Foret de Hennetiel. He was fiddling around wit' somethin' or other down by the Zoldeff River. I almost went down to check it out fer myself...but, you know, tight schedules 'n all.
        STUPID_COALITIONS_AND_THE_DAMN_WORK_THEY_GIVE                                 = 9207,  -- Stupid coalitions and the damn work they give me. I'd rather go fishing down there and see if I can catch another glimpse of 'em.
        MEMBER_WHAT_I_TOLD_YOU_DOWN_IN_FORET                                          = 9208,  -- 'Member what I told you--down in Foret de Hennetiel was the place I saw 'em.
        NOT_ANOTHER_PERSON_COMING_TO_ASK_ME_ABOUT                                     = 9209,  -- Not another person coming to ask me about leafkin!
        DON_T_TELL_ME_YOU_THINK_THEY_RE                                               = 9210,  -- Don't tell me you think they're adorable, too? Dumb creatures only get in my way.
        GET_THIS_I_WAS_IN_THE_YAHSE_HUNTING                                           = 9211,  -- Get this--I was in the Yahse Hunting Grounds, just minding my own business, see? And one of the stupid beasties hurls a rock at me!
        WHERE_YOU_ASK_HMM_LET_ME_TAKE_A                                               = 9212,  -- Where, you ask? Hmm... Let me take a look at my map... Yeah, somewhere around J-6.
        HEY_IF_YOU_WANT_TO_CHASE_EM_DOWN                                              = 9213,  -- Hey, if you want to chase 'em down, that's your call. Just don't come crying back to me if you end up with a couple lumps on your head.
        IF_YOU_REALLY_WANT_TO_SEE_A_LEAFKIN                                           = 9214,  -- If you really want to see a leafkin, try heading to the Yahse Hunting Grounds, near coordinates J-6. Just make sure to wear something hard on your head, ok?
        FIRST_MY_BACK_NOW_MY_SHOULDERS_SOMETIMES_I                                    = 9215,  -- First my back, now my shoulders... Sometimes I wonder if I'm really cut out for this sort of work.
        GOTTA_CATCH_ME_A_LOOK_AT_ONE_OF                                               = 9216,  -- Gotta catch me a look at one of those cute little creatures again someday.
        A_WORD_OF_ADVICE_IF_YOU_RE_INTERESTED                                         = 9217,  -- A word of advice: if you're interested in pioneering, you need to keep your body in tip-top shape.
        I_MEAN_REALLY_ALL_WET_BEHIND_THE_EARS                                         = 9218,  -- I mean, really. All wet behind the ears. No way you'll move up around here for years to come!
        ON_BEHALF_OF_THE_MUMMERS_COALITION_I_WELCOME                                  = 9219,  -- On behalf of the Mummers' Coalition, I welcome you to Adoulin.
        UNLIKE_THE_OTHER_COALITIONS_OUR_SUPPORT_OF_YOU                                = 9220,  -- Unlike the other coalitions, our support of you pioneers is rather indirect. We provide all manner of recreational and relaxation services to help you get back into the field well-rested and ready for action.
        ONE_OF_OUR_MORE_POPULAR_EVENTS_IS_THE                                         = 9221,  -- One of our more popular events is the raptor fights that occur periodically in the Watergarden Coliseum, located in Rala Waterways.
        WELL_AS_LONG_AS_YOU_RE_HERE_YOU                                               = 9222,  -- Well, as long as you're here, you might as well let me give you a brief description of them.
        I_LL_BET_YOU_RE_JUST_ITCHING_TO                                               = 9223,  -- I'll bet you're just itching to catch a glimpse of the excitement, aren't you?
        WELL_YOU_LL_BE_ABLE_TO_SCRATCH_THAT                                           = 9224,  -- Well, you'll be able to scratch that itch soon enough, for another bout is scheduled in the not-too-distant future. Just don't scream yourself hoarse rooting for one that catches your eye.
        THERE_WON_T_BE_ANY_NEED_TO_WORRY                                              = 9225,  -- There won't be any need to worry about that. The raptor tournament is going to be canceled.
        BUT_AREN_T_YOU_FROM_THE_PEACEKEEPERS_COALITION                                = 9226,  -- But--aren't you from the Peacekeepers' Coalition? On what grounds would you shut it down?
        ONE_OF_YOUR_RAPTORS_WENT_ON_A_BIT                                             = 9227,  -- One of your raptors went on a bit of a rampage. Call down Maester Flaviria immediately.
        A_RAMPAGE_WHAT_SORT_OF_LUNACY_IS_THIS                                         = 9228,  -- A rampage? What sort of lunacy is this!?
        WESLEY_THERE_YOU_ARE_WHERE_ON_VANA_DIEL                                       = 9229,  -- Wesley! There you are. Where on Vana'diel were you wandering around this whole time?
        MAESTER_FLAVIRIA                                                              = 9230,  -- Maester Flaviria...
        IMPECCABLE_TIMING_AS_ALWAYS_THERE_IS_A_MATTER                                 = 9231,  -- Impeccable timing, as always. There is a matter I wish to discuss.
        OH_WHAT_COULD_THE_PEACEKEEPERS_COALITION_WANT_WITH                            = 9232,  -- Oh? What could the Peacekeepers' Coalition want with me?
        AND_AT_SUCH_A_BUSY_TIME_WE_RE                                                 = 9233,  -- And at such a busy time! We're all running around like chocobos with our heads cut off preparing for the upcoming fights.
        MAESTER_HE_SAYS_THAT_ONE_OF_OUR_RAPTORS                                       = 9234,  -- Maester, he says that one of our raptors has caused a bit of an incident.
        INCIDENT_WHAT_S_THIS_NOW                                                      = 9235,  -- Incident? What's this now?
        ONE_OF_YOUR_RAPTORS_BROKE_OUT_OF_ITS                                          = 9236,  -- One of your raptors broke out of its stable and put some civilians in extreme danger.
        WE_MANAGED_TO_FIND_IT_BEFORE_IT_CAUSED                                        = 9237,  -- We managed to find it before it caused any real damage, but if we had been even a moment later...
        I_FIND_SUCH_BRAZEN_ACCUSATIONS_RATHER_HARD_TO                                 = 9238,  -- I find such brazen accusations rather hard to swallow, with Wesley there watching him the whole time.
        I_TURNED_MY_HEAD_AWAY_JUST_FOR_AN                                             = 9239,  -- I turned my head away just for an instant, and before I knew it...
        PREPOSTEROUS                                                                  = 9240,  -- Preposterous.
        IN_MY_OPINION_THE_SYSTEM_FOR_MONITORING_THOSE                                 = 9241,  -- In my opinion, the system for monitoring those creatures is wholly insufficient. It's only a matter of time before another one escapes...and next time we may not be so lucky. The Peacekeepers' Coalition sees no easy way to resolve this issue.
        ACCORDINGLY_WE_WOULD_LIKE_TO_ASK_FOR_YOUR                                     = 9242,  -- Accordingly, we would like to ask for your cooperation in discussing this matter. Please accompany me back to our headquarters so that my superiors may consult with you directly.
        FINE_AS_FOR_THE_TWO_OF_YOU_JUST                                               = 9243,  -- Fine. As for the two of you--just keep this between us. I don't want things to exacerbate an already tense situation.
        I_CAN_T_BELIEVE_IT                                                            = 9244,  -- I can't believe it.
        IT_IS_ALL_MY_RESPONSIBILITY_IF_I_HAD                                          = 9245,  -- It is all my responsibility. If I had been more careful...
        WESLEY_WHICH_ONE_BROKE_OUT                                                    = 9246,  -- Wesley, which one broke out?
        IT                                                                            = 9247,  -- It...
        IT_WAS_VORAHAL                                                                = 9248,  -- ...It was Vorahal.
        WHAT                                                                          = 9249,  -- What!?
        VORAHAL_MAY_BE_THE_FIERCEST_GLADIATOR_EVER_TO                                 = 9250,  -- Vorahal may be the fiercest gladiator ever to grace our raptor fights, but never once have I heard of him harming a soul outside the ring!
        BUT_WE_HAVE_NO_REASON_TO_DOUBT_THAT                                           = 9251,  -- But we have no reason to doubt that the Peacekeeper representative was telling us the truth.
        THEY_ALSO_SAY_THE_VICTIM_WAS_A_MAN                                            = 9252,  -- They also say the victim was a man in the residential district named Ilney.
        THEN_I_LL_GO_AND_ASK_HIM_TO                                                   = 9253,  -- Then I'll go and ask him to tell his story!
        B_BUT_THE_MAESTER_JUST_TOLD_US_TO                                             = 9254,  -- B-but...the Maester just told us to keep quiet and mind our own business!
        WE_VE_GOTTA_DO_SOMETHING                                                      = 9255,  -- We've gotta do something!
        E_EXCUSE_ME_SIR_MADAM                                                         = 9256,  -- E-excuse me, sir/madam]?
        FORGIVE_ME_FOR_GOING_ABOVE_MY_STATION_BUT                                     = 9257,  -- Forgive me for going above my station, but...
        BUT_SOMETHING_DOESN_T_SIT_RIGHT_THERE_S                                       = 9258,  -- ...But something doesn't sit right. There's no way that Vorahal would assault an innocent person.
        YOU_SEE_VORAHAL_ONCE_SAVED_HER_IN_HER                                         = 9259,  -- You see, Vorahal once saved her in her moment of need, when she was under attack by the creatures of the forest.
        THAT_S_WHAT_BROUGHT_VORAHAL_TO_THE_MUMMERS                                    = 9260,  -- That's what brought Vorahal to the Mummers' Coalition. I just KNOW there has to be some misunderstanding.
        PLEASE_I_BEG_OF_YOU_GO_TO_ILNEY                                               = 9261,  -- Please, I beg of you--go to Ilney, and listen to his story.
        THANK_YOU_SO_MUCH_I_PROBABLY_SHOULD_HAVE                                      = 9262,  -- Thank you so much! I probably should have asked this first, but what is your name?
        THANK_YOU_AGAIN_I_LL_BE_WAITING_HERE                                          = 9263,  -- Thank you again, %! I'll be waiting here for your report!
        I_LL_BE_HERE_WAITING_FOR_NEWS_FROM                                            = 9264,  -- I'll be here waiting for news from Ilney!
        HEADED_TO_THE_RESIDENTIAL_AREA_THEN_YOU_LL                                    = 9265,  -- Headed to the residential area? Then you'll wanna take that road over there.
        WHO_S_THERE                                                                   = 9266,  -- Who's there?
        WHAT_S_THIS_YOU_WANT_TO_HEAR_HOW                                              = 9267,  -- What's this? You want to hear how that fiendish raptor tried to tear me limb from limb?
        I_M_STILL_IN_SUCH_SHOCK_THAT_I                                                = 9268,  -- I'm still in such shock that I can barely form a coherent thought, but if you insist...
        HAVEN_T_SEEN_YOU_AROUND_THESE_PARTS_YOU                                       = 9269,  -- Haven't seen you around these parts. You one of those adventurers?
        SUPPOSE_THAT_S_NOT_IMPORTANT_YOU_CAME_TO                                      = 9270,  -- Suppose that's not important. You came to hear about the tragedy that has befallen me?
        I_LL_GET_STRAIGHT_TO_THE_POINT_FRESH                                          = 9271,  -- I'll get straight to the point. Fresh wounds and all.
        IT_WAS_AN_ORDINARY_MORNING_AND_I_WAS                                          = 9272,  -- It was an ordinary morning and I was heading off to market as usual.
        ON_MY_WAY_HOME_I_SAW_IT_RIGHT                                                 = 9273,  -- On my way home, I saw it right when I entered the residential district.
        WELL_I_WAS_DOWNRIGHT_SHOCKED_WHO_WOULDN_T                                     = 9274,  -- Well, I was downright shocked! Who wouldn't be? I tried to run, but my legs turned to jelly once it bared its cleaver-sized fangs at me!
        BEFORE_I_COULD_CALL_OUT_FOR_HELP_IT                                           = 9275,  -- Before I could call out for help, it jumped at me, and...well, you can see for yourself what state I'm in.
        COME_ON_HOW_DENSE_WOULD_YOU_HAVE_TO                                           = 9276,  -- Come on. How dense would you have to be to think that training monsters to fight for entertainment was a good idea?
        THE_MUMMERS_COALITION_WHAT_A_BUNCH_OF_FOOLS                                   = 9277,  -- The Mummers' Coalition? What a bunch of fools.
        THEY_SAY_THEY_WANT_PEOPLE_TO_HAVE_FUN                                         = 9278,  -- They say they want people to have fun, but that don't give 'em free reign to do whatever they want!
        ARRRRGH_MY_BACK_IT_S_LIKE_A_DAGGER                                            = 9279,  -- Arrrrgh, my back! It's like a dagger cuttin' down my spine!
        GOTTA_LIE_DOWN_FOR_A_BIT_IS_THAT                                              = 9280,  -- Gotta lie down for a bit. Is that all you needed to know? Then you can show yourself out.
        PARDON_ME_ARE_YOU_A_FRIEND_OF_ILNEY                                           = 9281,  -- Pardon me. Are you a friend of Ilney's?
        I_WAS_A_LITTLE_CONCERNED_BECAUSE_I_HAVEN                                      = 9282,  -- I was a little concerned, because I haven't seen him about recently.
        YOU_SAY_THAT_HE_RAN_INTO_A_BIT                                                = 9283,  -- You say that he ran into a bit of trouble with one of the Mummers' Coalition's raptors?
        THAT_WOULD_EXPLAIN_IT_I_LOVE_GOING_TO                                         = 9284,  -- That would explain it. I love going to watch those fights--a bit scary, but oh-so-thrilling!
        I_HAD_FIGURED_HE_TOOK_ILL_HE_HAD                                              = 9285,  -- I had figured he took ill. He had been walking around town with a bunch of rockberries, after all.
        ANY_QUESTIONS_WHAT_S_A_ROCKBERRY_NOTHING_IN                                   = 9286,  -- Any questions? What's a rockberry? Nothing in particular.
        PRETTY_MUCH_WHAT_THEIR_NAME_IMPLIES_BERRIES_AS                                = 9287,  -- Pretty much what their name implies--berries as hard as rock. Doesn't matter how healthy your teeth or how strong your jaw, they aren't fit for people to consume.
        WITH_ALL_THOSE_ROCKBERRIES_HE_MUST_HAVE_GOTTEN                                = 9288,  -- With all those rockberries, he must have gotten an upset stomach...at least, that's what I assumed.
        WELL_FORGIVE_MY_INTRUSION_I_LL_LET_YOU                                        = 9289,  -- Well, forgive my intrusion. I'll let you get back to your business.
        YOU_WENT_TO_ILNEY_S_HOUSE_FOR_ME                                              = 9290,  -- You went to Ilney's house for me? I knew I could trust you!
        HOW_WAS_HE                                                                    = 9291,  -- How was he?
        I_SEE_IF_HIS_WOUNDS_ARE_THAT_SEVERE                                           = 9292,  -- I see...if his wounds are that severe, then I guess it was Vorahal after all...
        ROCKBERRIES_ONE_OF_HIS_NEIGHBORS_SAID_HE_WAS                                  = 9293,  -- Rockberries!? One of his neighbors said he was carrying rockberries with him?
        RAPTORS_JUST_LOVE_ROCKBERRIES_WE_KEEP_A_SUPPLY                                = 9294,  -- Raptors just love rockberries. We keep a supply in the stable for them.
        THEY_AREN_T_PARTICULARLY_HEALTHY_FOR_THE_RAPTORS                              = 9295,  -- They aren't particularly healthy for the raptors though, so we save them as treats...much like you and I would eat cake. Mmm...cake.
        BUT_WHAT_WOULD_ILNEY_WANT_WITH_ROCKBERRIES                                    = 9296,  -- But what would Ilney want with rockberries?
        IS_WESLEY_THERE                                                               = 9297,  -- Is Wesley there?
