        IF_YOU_HURRY_YOU_MAY_STILL_BE_ABLE                                            = 9474,  -- If you hurry, you may still be able to catch her.
        MISTRESS_SVENJA_S_URGENT_BUSINESS_HAS_TAKEN_HER                               = 9475,  -- Mistress Svenja's urgent business has taken her to the Celennia Memorial Library.
        THAT_FACE_NOW_I_REMEMBER_YOU_CAME_HERE                                        = 9476,  -- That face... Now I remember. You came here earlier looking for Mistress Svenja, did you not?
        WHAT_AN_ODD_PLANT_YOU_HAVE_BROUGHT_WITH                                       = 9477,  -- What an odd plant you have brought with you. What would you have me do with it?
        YOU_MEAN_IT_HAS_CURATIVE_PROPERTIES_THAT_WILL                                 = 9478,  -- You mean it has curative properties that will help some poor young lad make a full recovery?
        THESE_ARE_THE_VERY_WORDS_OF_OUR_MISTRESS                                      = 9479,  -- These are the very words of our mistress herself? Then I shall see that she receives it right away.
        YOUR_EFFORTS_TO_AID_OUR_ORDER_ARE_GREATLY                                     = 9480,  -- Your efforts to aid our order are greatly appreciated, and most certainly deserve proper remuneration.
        ID_9481                                                                       = 9481,  -- ...
        THE_DOOR_IS_FIRMLY_SHUT                                                       = 9482,  -- The door is firmly shut.
        MISTRESS_SVENJA_IS_QUITE_BUSY_RESEARCHING_A_NEW                               = 9483,  -- Mistress Svenja is quite busy researching a new type of medicinal concoction. I'm afraid it will be a while before she is able to entertain visitors.
        WHY_WOULD_YOU_LOOK_WHO_IT_IS_HAVE                                             = 9484,  -- Why, would you look who it is! Have you brought some more % for our mistress?
        Y_YES_I_HAVE_WHERE_CAN_I_FIND                                                 = 9485,  -- Y-yes, I have. Where can I find her?
        I_HATE_TO_TURN_YOU_AWAY_AFTER_ALL                                             = 9486,  -- I hate to turn you away after all your generosity, but you must understand that she is quite busy these days.
        DO_NOT_FRET_I_WILL_MAKE_SURE_THEY                                             = 9487,  -- Do not fret--I will make sure they reach her.
        OH_I_SEE_THANK_YOU_VERY_MUCH                                                  = 9488,  -- Oh...I see. Thank you very much.
        OH_I_REMEMBER_YOU_YOU_ARE_THE_MAN                                             = 9489,  -- Oh, I remember you. You are the man/woman] who found some % for us, right?
        I_AM_SO_PLEASED_YOU_CAME_TO_SEE                                               = 9490,  -- I am so pleased you came to see us again. Thanks to your help, Mistress Svenja and other members of our order have begun looking for a cure for that poor lad.
        IT_WAS_NOT_THREE_DAYS_AGO_THAT_WE                                             = 9491,  -- It was not three days ago that we were able to give a concrete time frame for when the medicine will be ready. You should have seen the smile on his--Logan's--face.
        I_AM_A_BIT_EMBARRASSED_TO_ASK_YOU                                             = 9492,  -- I am a bit embarrassed to ask you such a question at this late juncture, but...I forgot to inquire as to your name.
        THANK_YOU_AGAIN_FOR_ALL_YOU_HAVE_DONE                                         = 9493,  -- %, thank you again for all you have done for us.
        LOGAN_MENTIONED_THAT_HE_WANTED_TO_EXPRESS_HIS                                 = 9494,  -- Logan mentioned that he wanted to express his gratitude directly, so I humbly ask that you do us the kindness of stopping by his residence.
        HE_IS_IN_THE_LOCAL_HOSPITAL_AT_PRESENT                                        = 9495,  -- He is in the local hospital at present. Just turn left and you'll find it.
        HM_JUST_WHO_ARE_YOU                                                           = 9496,  -- Hm? Just who are you?
        OHHH_YOU_RE_THE_ONE_WHO_FOUND_THE                                             = 9497,  -- Ohhh...you're the one who found the % for me.
        YOU_HAVE_MY_THANKS_I_SHOULD_BE_ABLE                                           = 9498,  -- You have my thanks. I should be able to head back out to the continent once they've completed my medicine.
        YOU_SEE_I_M_A_PIONEER_BEFORE_I                                                = 9499,  -- You see, I'm a pioneer. Before I got sick, I once whacked a morbol right upside the head with my pickaxe.
        COURSE_IT_BROKE_IN_HALF_THANKS_TO_THAT                                        = 9500,  -- 'Course, it broke in half thanks to that brute's thick hide, so she started scurrying back to whatever hole she crawled out of before I could finish the job. <Sigh> Just my luck.
        ANYWAY_I_WHIPPED_MY_TRUSTY_DAGGER_OUT_FROM                                    = 9501,  -- Anyway, I whipped my trusty dagger out from the side of my boot and stabbed her right as she turned around, but I must have jabbed it in there a bit too hard. Now it's gone. 'Twas my first weapon, too... What would my father say if he were alive to hear that I lost it...?
        WELL_ON_THE_BRIGHT_SIDE_AT_LEAST_I                                            = 9502,  -- Well, on the bright side, at least I have a goal to reach for once I get out of this infirmary.
        THAT_REMINDS_ME_I_NEED_TO_TELL_MY                                             = 9503,  -- ...That reminds me. I need to tell my leader that it won't be long before I report back to duty!
        IF_YOU_EVER_FIND_YOURSELF_IN_COULD_YOU                                        = 9504,  -- If you ever find yourself in %, could you stop by the frontier station and tell Borghest that I'll be back up and on my feet in no time?
        THANKS_FRIEND                                                                 = 9505,  -- Thanks, friend!
        A_PIONEER_WHAT_CAN_I_DO_FOR_YOU                                               = 9506,  -- A pioneer? What can I do for you today?
        YOU_WANT_US_TO_MAKE_A_PICKAXE_A                                               = 9507,  -- You want us to make...a pickaxe? A special request from Borghest, you say?
        AHA_IT_MUST_BE_FOR_THAT_YOUNG_LAD                                             = 9508,  -- Aha--it must be for that young lad who is supposed to return to duty soon. So you will need it sooner rather than later, then?
        LEAVE_IT_TO_ME_OR_RATHER_ONE_OF                                               = 9509,  -- Leave it to me! Or rather, one of our expert artisans. Let me just see if you've brought the materials we need... Yes, everything is in order.
        WE_RECEIVE_ALL_MANNER_OF_COMPLEX_ORDERS_DAY                                   = 9510,  -- We receive all manner of complex orders day in and day out, but something as simple as this will be ready in no time at all. Have a seat while we get to work.
        I_MUST_CONFESS_THAT_WAS_QUICKER_THAN_EVEN                                     = 9511,  -- I must confess, that was quicker than even I had anticipated. Here you are--a bona fide Inventors' Coalition original.
        I_WILL_NOT_CLAIM_THAT_IT_IS_CAPABLE                                           = 9512,  -- I will not claim that it is capable of mining every metal found in Vana'diel, but it should be more than sufficient for anything you find on the continent proper.
        THERE_IS_ONE_UNDENIABLE_TRUTH_ABOUT_CONSTRUCTION_THAT                         = 9513,  -- There is one undeniable truth about construction: that which is made can always be broken. However, I am confident in the durability of this piece.
        AS_LONG_AS_THE_BOY_MAKES_SURE_TO                                              = 9514,  -- As long as the boy makes sure to treat it with the proper care and respect, it should serve him well for many years to come.
        OH_MY_SOMETHING_AWFUL_HAS_HAPPENED_LOGAN_HAS                                  = 9515,  -- Oh my, %! Something awful has happened! Logan has suddenly taken a turn for the worse!
        IS_HE_STILL_CONSCIOUS                                                         = 9516,  -- Is he still conscious?
        HE_KEEPS_FADING_IN_AND_OUT_BUT_EVEN                                           = 9517,  -- He keeps fading in and out...but even when awake, he's completely non-responsive! Isn't the medicine ready yet!?
        I_WISH_I_HAD_BETTER_NEWS_BUT_THE                                              = 9518,  -- I wish I had better news, but...the extract we made contains a substance of unknown origin.
        IT_WOULD_BE_UNETHICAL_TO_ADMINISTER_THE_TREATMENT                             = 9519,  -- It would be unethical to administer the treatment until we determine its exact nature and effects.
        BUT_BUT                                                                       = 9520,  -- But...but...!
        THERE_S_NOTHING_ANY_OF_US_CAN_DO                                              = 9521,  -- There's nothing any of us can do right now. Pioneer, I must ask you to leave.
        A_PRESENT_FOR_THE_PATIENT_YOU_SAY_I                                           = 9522,  -- A present for the patient, you say? I'll hold on to it for now.
        YOU_MUST_GIVE_LOGAN_THE_REMEDY_LEST_HE                                        = 9523,  -- You must give Logan the remedy, lest he suffer even further!
        AS_I_SAID_BEFORE_WE_CANNOT_DO_ANYTHING                                        = 9524,  -- As I said before, we cannot do anything for him until we uncover what the strange substance contained in the mixture is.
        SUCH_A_CLAIM_IS_HOGWASH_I_CHECKED_THE                                         = 9525,  -- Such a claim is hogwash! I checked the medicine myself, and it contained no traces of any materials of unknown origin.
        WHAT_ARE_YOU                                                                  = 9526,  -- What are you--
        OTHELLIUS_THINK_BACK_TO_TEN_YEARS_AGO_SURELY                                  = 9527,  -- Othellius, think back to ten years ago...surely you can't have forgotten?
        IT_DOESN_T_HAVE_TO_BE_THAT_WAY                                                = 9528,  -- It doesn't have to be that way again. Colonization isn't forbidden anymore! We must do all that we can.
        TO_BE_SURE_TIMES_HAVE_CHANGED_PERHAPS_MORE                                    = 9529,  -- To be sure, times have changed. Perhaps more than any of us realize.
        HAVE_YOU_COME_TO_PAY_US_A_VISIT                                               = 9530,  -- ...%, have you come to pay us a visit once more?
        IT_IS_MY_SWORN_DUTY_TO_TEND_TO                                                = 9531,  -- It is my sworn duty to tend to the ills of the populace. But this, being prevented from upholding my oath...nothing is more infuriating.
        THOUGH_THE_BRIGHT_LIGHT_OF_COLONIZATION_SHINES_DOWN                           = 9532,  -- Though the bright light of colonization shines down on us once more, the darkness of the past continues to cloud the present.
        WHAT_DO_YOU_WISH_TO_KNOW_WHAT_HAPPENED                                        = 9533,  -- What do you wish to know? What happened ten years ago? How is the medicine coming along?
        NEARLY_TEN_YEARS_AGO_A_YOUNG_MAN_OF                                           = 9534,  -- Nearly ten years ago, a young man of simple upbringing was stricken with a terrible disease.
        THE_HEALERS_OF_OUR_ORDER_DID_THEIR_UTMOST                                     = 9535,  -- The healers of our order did their utmost to bring him back to health, but they succeeded in relieving but a portion of the symptoms.
        THE_LAD_S_GRANDFATHER_FRAUGHT_WITH_GRIEF_BROKE                                = 9536,  -- The lad's grandfather, fraught with grief, broke the nation's most sacred of laws by venturing out into the wilds in search of an herbal remedy.
        YET_NEVER_DID_HE_RETURN_TO_THE_CITY                                           = 9537,  -- Yet never did he return to the city.
        IT_WAS_NOT_LONG_AFTER_THAT_THE_GRANDSON                                       = 9538,  -- It was not long after that the grandson finally found solace in Altana's eternal embrace.
        WOULD_THAT_THE_TRAGEDY_HAD_STOPPED_THERE_THE                                  = 9539,  -- Would that the tragedy had stopped there. The sickness spread, and as medicines were hard to procure, many of Adoulin's finest suffered needlessly.
        AND_NOW_THAT_WE_HAVE_THE_CHANCE_TO                                            = 9540,  -- And now that we have the chance to save Logan...I cannot bear to have history repeat itself!
        OTHELLIUS_INSISTS_THAT_WE_CANNOT_ADMINISTER_THE_MEDICINE                      = 9541,  -- Othellius insists that we cannot administer the medicine until we discover what this strange substance is, but my examinations have revealed nothing out of the ordinary.
        COULD_THERE_BE_ANOTHER_REASON_FOR_HIS_HESITATION                              = 9542,  -- Could there be another reason for his hesitation to administer the remedy?
        HMM_MAYBE_I_SHOULD_HAVE_MARGRET_OF_THE                                        = 9543,  -- Hmm...maybe I should have Margret of the Scouts' Coalition see if she can find out anything.
        IF_WE_KNOW_WHAT_GIVES_HIM_PAUSE_PERHAPS                                       = 9544,  -- If we know what gives him pause, perhaps we can bring him around.
        I_HAVE_THE_UTMOST_CONFIDENCE_THAT_SHE_WILL                                    = 9545,  -- I have the utmost confidence that she will lend us her aid. After all, she did so the last time Svenja entreated her.
        I_CANNOT_SPARE_ANY_MORE_TIME_AWAY_FROM                                        = 9546,  -- I cannot spare any more time away from my charges, %, so may I ask you to visit Margret in my stead?
        THINK_OF_IT_AS_A_FAVOR_NOT_FOR                                                = 9547,  -- Think of it as a favor not for me, but for a man who needs you now more than ever.
        OH_YOU_RE_A_SIGHT_FOR_SORE_EYES                                               = 9548,  -- %! Oh, you're a sight for sore eyes!
        WAS_MARGRET_S_SEARCH_SUCCESSFUL_DID_YOU_FIND                                  = 9549,  -- Was Margret's search successful? Did you find out anything about Logan's medicine?
        WHAT_IS_YOUR_RESPONSE_TELL_HER_WHAT_YOU                                       = 9550,  -- What is your response? Tell her what you learned. Say you didn't find anything out.
        N_NO_THERE_S_NO_WAY_MISTRESS_SVENJA                                           = 9551,  -- N-no...there's no way Mistress Svenja would say something like that!
        ALIANNE_WHAT_S_WRONG                                                          = 9552,  -- Alianne? What's wrong?
        MISTRESS_JUST_TELL_ME_WHY_WHY_WON_T                                           = 9553,  -- Mistress... Just tell me why...why won't you administer the antidote to Logan?
        HAS_OTHELLIUS_NOT_TOLD_YOU_WE_HAVE_NOT                                        = 9554,  -- Has Othellius not told you? We have not properly tested it, and thus it is not safe for human use.
        IS_THAT_THE_TRUTH_OR_ARE_YOU_AFRAID                                           = 9555,  -- Is that the truth? Or are you afraid that its success might bolster colonization supporters? Is that not the real reason you are risking the life of this poor boy?
        ALIANNE_YOU_COULD_NOT_POSSIBLY_THINK_I                                        = 9556,  -- Alianne, you could not possibly think I--
        MISTRESS_SVENJA_WE_ALL_KNOW_OF_YOUR_DISTASTE                                  = 9557,  -- Mistress Svenja, we all know of your distaste for colonization and the threat it poses to the security of our city.
        BUT_TO_TURN_YOUR_BACK_ON_THOSE_WHO                                            = 9558,  -- But to turn your back on those who suffer for the sake of making a political statement! I just...I...I...
        ALIANNE                                                                       = 9559,  -- Alianne!
        ALIANNE_COME_BACK                                                             = 9560,  -- Alianne, come back!
        WHAT_WHAT_COULD_POSSIBLY_HAVE_HAPPENED_TO_MAKE                                = 9561,  -- What...what could possibly have happened to make her say such a horrible thing?
        SHE_ASKED_YOU_TO_ENLIST_MARGRET_S_AID                                         = 9562,  -- She asked you to enlist Margret's aid?
        I_SUPPOSE_IT_IS_MY_FAULT_FOR_NOT                                              = 9563,  -- I suppose it is my fault for not giving her a thoughtful explanation.
        I_CAN_ONLY_IMAGINE_THE_CONSTERNATION_THIS_INCIDENT                            = 9564,  -- I can only imagine the consternation this incident has caused you. Here, as recompense for your trouble.
        I_CAN_ONLY_IMAGINE_THE_CONSTERNATION_THIS_INCIDENT_2                          = 9565,  -- %, I can only imagine the consternation this incident has caused you. Here, as recompense for your trouble.
        IN_MY_ATTEMPTS_TO_BOTH_SAVE_THE_LIFE                                          = 9566,  -- In my attempts to both save the life of the ill and protect the citizens from harm, I have failed to achieve either. What's worse, both are slipping further from my grasp.
        I_HAVE_FAILED_NOT_JUST_AS_LEADER_OF                                           = 9567,  -- I have failed, not just as leader of the Order of Janniston, but also as a practitioner of the healing arts...
        I_WAS_CONFIDENT_THAT_ONE_AS_TALENTED_AS                                       = 9568,  -- I was confident that one as talented as Margret would come up with answers, but to think that even she failed...
        LOGAN_SUFFERS_MORE_WITH_EACH_PASSING_MOMENT_WHAT                              = 9569,  -- Logan suffers more with each passing moment. What am I to do?
        OH_FORGIVE_ME_FOR_NOT_THANKING_YOU_PROPERLY                                   = 9570,  -- Oh, %...forgive me for not thanking you properly.
        YOUR_AID_IN_THIS_CRUCIAL_MOMENT_MEANS_THE                                     = 9571,  -- Your aid in this crucial moment means the world to me--and to Logan. Here, for you.
        I_MUST_CONVINCE_SVENJA_TO_APPROVE_THE_MEDICINE                                = 9572,  -- I must convince Svenja to approve the medicine. It's the only way to save the boy's life.
        YET_I_AM_BUT_A_HUMBLE_SERVANT_SO                                              = 9573,  -- Yet I am but a humble servant, so how...?
        AND_YOU_ARE_OH_YES_THE_PIONEER_KNOWN                                          = 9574,  -- And you are...? Oh, yes, the pioneer known as %.
        HERE_TO_SEE_ALIANNE_CORRECT_UNFORTUNATELY_SHE_HAS                             = 9575,  -- Here to see Alianne, correct? Unfortunately, she has been dispatched to Yorcia Weald to deal with reports of pioneers suddenly taking ill.
        HOW_FORTUITOUS_THAT_I_CATCH_YOU_IN_YOUR                                       = 9576,  -- How fortuitous that I catch you in your manse, Svenja.
        MARGRET_TO_WHAT_DO_I_OWE_THE_HONOR                                            = 9577,  -- Margret? To what do I owe the honor?
        I_HAVE_FINISHED_DECIPHERING_THE_WEATHERED_TOME_YOU                            = 9578,  -- I have finished deciphering the weathered tome you asked me about, and I'm afraid the situation is grave. It states that a plague nearly rent Adoulin in twain during the time of the Great Expedition.
        A_PLAGUE_HOW_COULD_SUCH_A_CALAMITOUS_EVENT                                    = 9579,  -- A plague!? How could such a calamitous event be erased from our collective consciousness?
        I_CANNOT_SAY_YET_IT_SEEMS_THAT_THIS                                           = 9580,  -- I cannot say--yet it seems that this was no ordinary malady. More than half of those infected did not live to see the next turn of the moon, and by all accounts it was the largest disaster to befall Adoulin since the city's founding.
        THE_FIRST_VICTIM_CLAIMED_WAS_A_PIONEER_AND                                    = 9581,  -- The first victim claimed was a pioneer, and in response the king ordered the surrounding jungle burned to the ground. The exact cause was never found, but the arboreal sacrifice appeared to have its intended effect.
        SOME_HAVE_ASSERTED_THAT_THE_CONSUMPTION_OF_AN                                 = 9582,  -- Some have asserted that the consumption of an unclassified species of plant was the catalyst, and that the king was persuaded by their arguments.
        I_CANNOT_HELP_BUT_WONDER_IF_THIS_IS                                           = 9583,  -- I cannot help but wonder if this is related to the situation with Logan.
        OTHELLIUS_WE_CANNOT_WAIT_ANY_LONGER_ADMINISTER_THE                            = 9584,  -- Othellius, we cannot wait any longer. Administer the draught, now!
        BUT_MISTRESS_SVENJA_OUR_TESTS_ARE_NOT_YET                                     = 9585,  -- But Mistress Svenja, our tests are not yet--
        THE_TIME_FOR_TESTING_HAS_PASSED_WE_MUST                                       = 9586,  -- The time for testing has passed. We must do all that we can for him.
        EXERCISE_CAUTION_WITH_THE_DOSAGE_HOWEVER_WE_CANNOT                            = 9587,  -- Exercise caution with the dosage, however. We cannot be fully certain that nothing will go wrong.
        O_OF_COURSE_2                                                                 = 9588,  -- O-of course.
        THIS_BODES_ILL_FOR_ALIANNE_AS_WELL_I                                          = 9589,  -- %, this bodes ill for Alianne as well. I bid you make haste for the frontier station in Yorcia Weald.
        THERE_IS_NOT_A_MOMENT_TO_LOSE                                                 = 9590,  -- There is not a moment to lose!
        ARI_BARALI_WHAT_HAS                                                           = 9591,  -- Ari-Barali! What has--?
        M_MISTRESS_SVENJA_I                                                           = 9592,  -- M-Mistress Svenja...I...
        SHHH_SAVE_YOUR_ENERGY_LITTLE_ONE_TRUST_YOURSELF                               = 9593,  -- Shhh. Save your energy, little one. Trust yourself to our care, and you will be up and well before the next trading vessel arrives.
        OTHELLIUS_TAKE_HIM_INSIDE                                                     = 9594,  -- Othellius, take him inside.
        IT_IS_NOT_LIKE_YOU_TO_BE_SO                                                   = 9595,  -- %? It is not like you to be so harried. Is aught amiss?
        ALIANNE_NO_NOT_HER                                                            = 9596,  -- Alianne!? No, not her...
        YOU_RE_RIGHT_A_CITY_S_LEADERS_MUST                                            = 9597,  -- ...You're right. A city's leaders must remain strong in times of crisis.
        I_WILL_DISPATCH_MY_MOST_TALENTED_HERBALISTS_TO                                = 9598,  -- I will dispatch my most talented herbalists to the continent's frontier stations posthaste.
        AS_FOR_THE_LAD_LOGAN_I_WISH_I                                                 = 9599,  -- As for the lad, Logan...I wish I could offer better news, but there is yet no change in his condition.
        WERE_I_A_FAITH_HEALER_I_WOULD_BE                                              = 9600,  -- Were I a faith healer, I would be beseeching the Goddess's aid, but I can only trust that our remedy will have its intended effects.
        SHOULD_THESE_INCIDENTS_BE_LINKED_AND_I_HAVE                                   = 9601,  -- Should these incidents be linked--and I have little doubt they are--we will require copious amounts of % just to tread water.
        I_FEAR_I_WILL_BE_CALLING_ON_YOU                                               = 9602,  -- I fear I will be calling on you again in the weeks and months ahead. Consider this payment in advance.
        SUCH_A_CONTAGIOUS_MALADY_CASTS_A_SHADOW_ON                                    = 9603,  -- Such a contagious malady casts a shadow on the future of our city. I dare not imagine what will happen should we fail to root out the cause.
        FRIENDS_COMPATRIOTS_THE_TIME_HAS_COME_TO_FREE                                 = 9604,  -- Friends! Compatriots! The time has come to free our city from the shackles of the nefarious Blackthorn Coven!
        THEY_HAVE_BLIGHTED_ULBUKA_FOR_TOO_LONG_AND                                    = 9605,  -- They have blighted Ulbuka for too long, and now count the scaly Velkk amongst their most valued allies. None of us are safe while they roam free!
        IT_IS_BY_OUR_HANDS_THAT_EVIL_MUST                                             = 9606,  -- It is by our hands that evil must be banished to whence it came. To arms, brothers and sisters!
        ID_9607                                                                       = 9607,  -- %!
        I_ALMOST_REGURGITATED_MY_LUNCH_ARAUSTOIX_IS_PLANNING                          = 9608,  -- I almost regurgitated my lunch--Araustoix is planning on flaying the Blackthorn Coven alive!
        THEY_PROMISED_US_THEY_WERE_NO_LONGER_IN                                       = 9609,  -- They promised us they were no longer in cahoots with those savage brutes, but now Vortimere has authorized an expedition to expunge them from the continent.
        WE_VE_GOT_TO_WARN_SORAA_AND_HER                                               = 9610,  -- We've got to warn Soraa and her fellowship before they get burned to a crisp!
        LET_S_SEE_IF_WE_CAN_FIND_THEM                                                 = 9611,  -- Let's see if we can find them at their usual haunt--near J-6 in Yorcia Weald!
        IF_I_HAD_TEN_GIL_FOR_HOW_MANY                                                 = 9612,  -- If I had ten gil for how many times I've told you to keep a close eye on your suborrrdinates, Svenja, I'd be a rich woman! They've all come down with whatever that plague of yours is while out searching for %.
        YOU_MAY_BE_CONTENT_FILLING_BEDS_IN_THAT                                       = 9613,  -- You may be content filling beds in that infirrrmary of yours, but I refuse to subject any of my coalition's staff to your every whim.
        AND_EVEN_IF_I_DID_SEND_OUT_A                                                  = 9614,  -- And even if I did send out a whole regiment, eventually we'd pluck the jungle dry.
        CHALVAVA_MAY_I_PLEASE_HAVE_AN_UPDATE_ON                                       = 9615,  -- Chalvava, may I please have an update on your progress?
        THE_ARBORETUM_S_BEST_MINDS_HAVE_BEEN_TOILING                                  = 9616,  -- The arboretum's best minds have been toiling day and night, Mistress Svenja, and though our tomatoes have borne fruit, I can't say the same about your hennebloom leaves.
        WOULD_THAT_YOU_HAD_BROUGHT_ME_BETTER_NEWS                                     = 9617,  -- Would that you had brought me better news... I humbly request your aid--both of your aid--in continuing to pursue this mystery.
        SVENJA_I_APOLOGIZE_FOR_COMING_OFF_SO_HARRRSHLY                                = 9618,  -- Svenja, I apologize for coming off so harrrshly. Keep your chin up.
        THANK_YOU_LHE                                                                 = 9619,  -- Thank you, Lhe.
        YOU_ARE_A_SIGHT_FOR_SORE_EYES_IN                                              = 9620,  -- %. You are a sight for sore eyes in these troubling times.
        INQUIRE_ABOUT_WHAT_ALIANNE_S_HEALTH_THE_CONTAGIOUS                            = 9621,  -- Inquire about what? Alianne's health. The contagious malady.
        I_FEAR_SHE_REMAINS_COMATOSE_AND_HER_ODDS                                      = 9622,  -- I fear she remains comatose, and her odds of recovery are grim.
        THE_SIGNS_OF_THE_PLAGUE_ARE_THERE_IN                                          = 9623,  -- The signs of the plague are there in full. She spent so much time watching out for others that she forgot to take care of herself.
        I_HAD_WARNED_HER_THAT_SHE_WOULD_BE                                            = 9624,  -- I had warned her that she would be unable to fulfill her charge should she herself succumb, yet...
        I_HAVE_REQUESTED_THAT_ALL_FRONTIER_STATION_STAFF                              = 9625,  -- I have requested that all frontier station staff pour resources into investigating the exact cause, but we remain empty-handed.
        IT_IS_OF_LITTLE_COMFORT_THAT_WE_HAVE                                          = 9626,  -- It is of little comfort that we have been able to stop the illness from progressing in the afflicted, thanks in no small part to your previous assistance.
        MISTRESS_SVENJA                                                               = 9627,  -- Mistress Svenja!
        OTHELLIUS_SHOULD_YOU_NOT_BE_AT_THE_INFIRMARY                                  = 9628,  -- Othellius? Should you not be at the infirmary?
        I_HAD_BEEN_BUT_THEN_LOGAN_DISAPPEARED_AND                                     = 9629,  -- I had been...but then Logan disappeared, and I figured he may have come this way.
