        A_TRUE_PIONEER_IS_NOT_JUST_ABOUT_COLONIZING                                   = 9696,  -- A true pioneer is not just about...colonizing and clearing a path for humanity. A true pioneer...guides people away from harm and...protects them in times of danger.
