        I_M_NOT_COMPLETELY_SURE_BUT_THIS_MIGHT                                        = 11379,  -- I'm not completely sure, but this might help set some things straight...I guess.
        LET_ME_ADD_ONE_THING_PLEASE_FIND_IT                                           = 11380,  -- Let me add one thing. Please find it within your heart of hearts to give me anything of particular interest you get from completing objectives.
        I_LL_MAKE_IT_WORTH_YOUR_WHILE_I                                               = 11381,  -- I'll make it worth your while...I swear! Just keep at it and I'll be sure to surprise you with a hot, steaming helping of gratitude one day.
