        IS_THE_OKAY_YES_NO_2                                                          = 11451,  -- Is the [/Argosy Armor/Hesychast's Attire/Piety Attire/Archmage's Attire/Vitiation Attire/Plunderer's Attire/Caballarius Armor/Fallen's Armor/Ankusa Armor/Bihu Attire/Arcadian Attire/Sakonji Armor/Mochizuki Garb/Pteroslaver Armor/Glyphic Attire/Luhlaza Attire/Lanun Attire/Pitre Attire/Horos Attire/Pedagogy Attire/Bagua Attire/Futhrak Attire] okay? Yes. No.
