        WHAT_WILL_YOU_DO_NOTHING_ASK_ABOUT                                            = 12039,  -- What will you do? ([Bayld/Obs. Frag./Corpuscles]: #) Nothing. [Proceed with the exchange/Learn about augmentation/Proceed with the exchange/Proceed with the exchange]. [@/Check augmentable equipment/@/@]. [@/Check arcane glyptic materials/@/@]. Ask about [ergon tinctures/arcane glyptics/obsidian fragments/mweya plasm].
        WHAT_SAY_YOU_TO_LOOKING_OVER_OUR_SELECTION                                    = 12040,  -- What say you to looking over our selection of Pioneers' Coalition tools?
