        ALWAYS_BE_PREPARED_THAT_S_ONE_OF_THE                                          = 12056,  -- Always be prepared. That's one of the Scouts' Coalition's many mottos, especially when it comes to spoils! I can tell you exactly how sweet victory will taste!
