        DO_YOU_WISH_TO_HAVE_THE_EQUIPMENT_YOU                                         = 12067,  -- Do you wish to have the equipment you wrested from the clutches of the continent's menaces bestowed with certain arcane glyptics? If not, your soul will forever be consumed with regret.
