        IF_YOU_ENJOY_TOSSING_DICE_EVERY_SO_OFTEN                                      = 12185,  -- If you enjoy tossing dice every so often, this may just be the challenge you have been searching for. Who shall reach 11 with a few flicks of the wrist first--you or me?
        EITHER_YOU_OR_I_MAY_CHOOSE_TO_SHOOT                                           = 12186,  -- Either you or I may choose to shoot and roll the dice, stay and do nothing, or pick from three tricks up your sleeve.
        THE_THREE_TRICKS_IN_YOUR_ARSENAL_OF_DECEPTION_2                               = 12187,  -- The three tricks in your arsenal of deception include Sneak Peek, which allows you to see your opponent's shots, using the old Switcheroo and trading shots with your opponent, or forcing your opponent to reroll a shot of his choice with Crooked Die.
        THESE_THREE_TRICKS_WILL_SPIN_THE_WHEEL_OF_2                                   = 12188,  -- These three tricks will spin the wheel of fortune in your favor, but it is precisely because of their immense powers that we must limit their use to once per game.
