        ITCHING_TO_KNOW_ABOUT_EITHER_FRONTIER_BIVOUACS_CONSTRUCTION                   = 12267,  -- Itching to know about either frontier bivouacs' construction status or durability? Then you have come to the right person, sir/ma'am].
