        FRONTIER_BIVOUAC_IS_CURRENTLY_AT_PERCENT_DURABILITY                           = 12270,  -- Frontier Bivouac[/ #1/ #2/ #3/ #4/ #5] is currently at # percent durability. [It's in dire need of immediate frontline support!/I highly suggest providing frontline support to it in the near future./You might want to think about providing frontline support to it eventually./It seems relatively sturdy./It's still sturdy enough that you have nothing to worry about.]
