        DERE_WE_GOES_OHO_LOOKS_LIKE_IT_DON                                            = 12817,  -- Dere we goes. Oho, looks like it don't wants no more. Guess ya gotta come back tomorrow if ya's wanna keep gettin' rid o' stuff.
