        NAH_IT_JUST_WON_T_WOIK_I_S                                                    = 12821,  -- Nah, it just won't woik. I's did my best, but yer daily tally just won't go no higher. Ya ain't gonna get no prizes by hoardin' yer points, so stop bein' such a Greedalox and use 'em.
        GIL_LOVIN_GOBBIES_YA_S_HIT_DA_JACKPOT                                         = 12822,  -- Gil-lovin' Gobbies, %, ya's hit da jackpot! I's so happy for ya I think I's gettin' da vapors.
