        WHOAWHOAWHOA_IF_YA_S_GOT_BUSINESS_WIT_DA                                      = 12824,  -- Whoawhoawhoa! If ya's got business wit' da box, ya foist gots business wit' me. Whatcha need?
        SO_YA_BE_WANTIN_THE_SPECIAL_DIAL_WHOAWHOAWHOA                                 = 12825,  -- So ya be wantin' the special dial? Whoawhoawhoa! Get yer grubby hands offa that! Ya don't have enough daily tally, and I's not 'bout tah let ya cheat me!
        SO_YA_BE_WANTIN_THE_DIAL_M_KAY                                                = 12826,  -- So ya be wantin' the [special/Adoulin/pictlogica/Wanted/campaign] dial? M'kay, get yerself all steeled up, 'cause here we go! 'Member, no complaints!
        SO_YA_BE_WANTIN_THE_DIAL_WHOAWHOAWHOA_GET                                     = 12827,  -- So ya be wantin' the [special/Adoulin/pictlogica/Wanted] dial? Whoawhoawhoa! Get yer grubby hands offa that! I's already opened one fer ya today! Haul that keister outta here and come back t'morrow.
        OY_WOULD_YA_GET_A_LOOK_AT_YER                                                 = 12828,  -- Oy, would ya get a look at yer %! I guess I can let ya open [/Dial 1/Dial 2/Dial 3/Dial 4/Dial 5/the special dial///the abjuration dial/the fortune dial/the furnishings dial//the Vana'versary dial/the festival dial] whenever ya want fer not a single onz o' daily tally!
        DUN_THINK_THAT_I_S_BE_A_GIL                                                   = 12829,  -- Dun think that I's be a gil-grubbin' good-fer-nuthin'. If'n ya dun wanna open any dial, then I gives ya back yer %.
        YER_EYES_BE_BIGGER_N_YER_STOMACH_IF                                           = 12830,  -- Yer eyes be bigger'n yer stomach. If'n ya wanna open [/Dial 1/Dial 2/Dial 3/Dial 4/Dial 5/the Special Dial///the abjuration dial/the fortune dial/the furnishings dial//the Vana'versary dial/the festival diaal] usin' yer %, then ya gotta make room in yer bags!
